data.description: If you're looking for a spacious and cozy home with lots of upgrades, you don't want to miss this 3 bed/2 bath property that has everything you need and more. Freshly painted, this home features hardwood floors throughout the main level. The kitchen is perfect for entertaining, featuring oversized granite island and counters, 42" cabinets, and stainless appliances. Walk through the front door and you will feel the spaciousness of this home - the family room is warm and inviting, with a gas log fireplace and tons of natural light. The master bedroom has a walk-in closet and an updated, ensuite bathroom. The partial basement is finished with three additional rooms that can be used as offices, a music studio or playrooms. The large laundry room on main leaves plenty of room for additional storage on the lower level. The enclosed garage is heated and cooled - with tons of natural late this is an ideal space for an art studio, a home gym, or a workshop. The large deck is perfect for entertaining, overlooking the private back yard that has mature trees and landscaping. This home is located in a quiet neighborhood - a rare find at an unbeatable price - don't let it slip away!
